Runs foo.nu in the current context.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> source foo.nu


```
Runs foo.nu in current context and call the command defined, suppose foo.nu has content: 
``def say-hi [] { echo 'Hi!' }``
.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> source ./foo.nu; say-hi


```
Sourcing 
``null``
